cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on face verification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach is based on a discriminative Gaussian process latent variable model, which involves machine learning techniques such as multi-task learning (cs.LG), and can adapt to complex data distributions (cs.AI). The experiments involve extensive use of image and video data (cs.MM), and the model is trained using multiple sources of data (cs.NE).
